data.description: Great location, walking distance to elementary, sports complex, Casey's, and community park. With some updates this 3 bd, 2 bath home located on almost a half acre lot can be the best home for a young family. Home has mature trees and lots of privacy. This home has a great backyard for grilling, parties, and playing. Come see this one before it is gone!
